## Tree.commitTransaction() method

> This API is provided as a preview for developers and may change based on feedback that we receive. Do not use this API in a production environment.
> 

Commits the currently open transaction. In case there are no other transactions running a new version of the tree is persisted.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
commitTransaction(): Promise<void>;
```
<b>Returns:</b>

Promise&lt;void&gt;
